{"tid":1563066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方證實警員舞棍片段屬實　去年二月拍　和向休班警派警棍「完全無關係」","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:15.000Z","uid":68738,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97069f260d4afabf5ac0f90f422731a064deb002","tid":1563066,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kongwingcheung-13_xeXtc_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkongwingcheung-13_xeXtc_1200x0.png&h=03aa4234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方星期二公布將向休班警員派發警棍，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥強調，休班警員不會亂用警棍，「休班同事唔會無端端攞裝備嚟玩」；當晚網上流傳一段，懷疑警員在警局內揮舞警棍的片段。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥今日在警方記者會證實，片段中的確實是警員，片段是在 2018 年 2 月，由「某差館」的槍房警員拍攝，「同今次向休班警員派發警棍完全無關係」；他承認片段中警員的行為「唔理想」，相關警區會跟進了解。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調無論當值或休班的警員都會認真處理裝備，使用時要解釋用途，亦要為自行的行為負責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%88%9E%E6%A3%8D%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E5%B1%AC%E5%AF%A6-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%88%E6%8B%8D-%E5%92%8C%E5%90%91%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%84%A1%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2588%259E%25E6%25A3%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%258B%258D-%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb5a4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=39d66c96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25AD%258